#   2. Re-ingest with ENABLE_CONTEXTUAL_RETRIEVAL=true and the Haiku-class
#      endpoint configured. Run the same eval. Compare hit@k / MRR.
#
# Schema matches data/eval/golden.jsonl. Update expectedSubstrings to
# match the verbatim wording in your copy of the book — current values
# are common phrasings that work for most ML history texts.
#
